  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Urgent Intevention in WASH Cluster for (3) Yemeni Governorates</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In line with the national Water, Sanitation, and Hygiene (WASH) Cluster strategy, IOM seeks to improve the living conditions of internally displaced persons by restoring access to safe water, sanitation, and hygiene services. IOM&#x2019;s WASH solutions are immediate, scalable, and sustainable, with the overall aim of reducing morbidity and mortality rates and the spread of water borne diseases among communities affected by the ongoing conflict.</narrative>
  </description>
